10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">The Visitor understands and
  acknowledges that the Company's trade secrets consist of information and
  materials that are valuable and not generally known by the Company's
  competitors. The Company's trade secrets include:</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" mce_style="margin-left:.75in;text-indent:-.25in;tab-stops:list .75in"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;" mce_style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;"><span mce_="mce_">a.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;" mce_style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;" mce_style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Any
  and all information concerning the Company's current, future or proposed
  products, including, but not limited to, unpublished computer code (both source
  code and object code), drawings, specifications, notebook entries, technical
  notes and graphs, computer printouts, technical memoranda and correspondence,
  product development agreements and related agreements.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" mce_style="margin-left:.75in;text-indent:-.25in;tab-stops:list .75in"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;" mce_style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;"><span mce_="mce_">b.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;" mce_style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;" mce_style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Information
  and materials relating to the Company's purchasing, accounting and marketing;
  including, but not limited to, marketing plans, sales data, unpublished
  promotional material, cost and pricing information and customer lists.</span></p>
<p class="MsoNormal" mce_style="margin-left:.75in;text-indent:-.25in;tab-stops:list .75in"><span style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;" mce_style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;;"><span mce_="mce_">c.<span style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;" mce_style="font:7.0pt &quot;Times New Roman&quot;">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;" mce_style="font-size:10.0pt;font-family:&quot;Arial&quot;,&quot;sans-serif&quot;">Information
